('App\\Model\\Product', 158, 'bd', 'description', '<h2>Product details of sharaban Nano Mist Sprayer Nano Facial Mister Portable Mini Face Mist Handy Sprayer Atomization Eyelash Extensions Cool Facial Steamer for Skin Care USB Rechargeable</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Material: ABS</li>\r\n	<li>Battery capacity: 550mAh</li>\r\n	<li>Water tank capacity: 30 ml</li>\r\n	<li>Charging time: 2 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 9 x 4 cm</li>\r\n	<li>Connector type: USB</li>\r\n	<li>Color: white / pink/black/green</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AboutThis&nbsp;Item</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We aim to show you accurate product information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Manufacturers,suppliers and others provide what you see here, and we have not verifiedit.&nbsp;See our disclaimer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product description Nanosprayer nano facial mister portable mini face mist handy sprayer atomizationeyelash extensions cool facial steamer for skin care usb rechargeableFeatures:Easy to carry:Our product is small in size and easy to carry, this facial moisturizer can bringyou convenience whether you are going shopping, travelling or on businesstrips, it will make you feel relaxed and cool in the hot weather and keep theskin hydrated in winter.Ideal gift:There are different colors of this portable mini face mist handy sprayer and 4USB charging cables, you can share this facial sprayer to your family orfriends as a gift, come and enjoy this cool moment in summer and keep your facemoisturized in winter.Specifications:Material: ABS plasticColor: as the pictures shownCapacity: 30 mlSize:Product size: 10 x 4 x 4 cm / 3.94 x 1.57 x 1.57 inchesPackage size: 14.5 x 4 x 4 cm/ 5.7 x 1.57 x 1.57 inchesPackage includes:1 x Nano facial spray1 x USB cableWarm note:Please add mineral water,do not add distilled water, viscous liquid, essential oil, etc., otherwise itwill cause water droplets in the nozzle.Remember to adjust the ratio when adding alcohol, perfume, and milk.Manual measurement, please allow slight errors on size.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;1.Note: please addmineral water to the spray, do not add pure water, distilled water, essentialoils, hydrosols, viscous liquids, etc., because whether the water density istoo high or too low, it will lead to poor atomization and water droplets or blockagein the spray nozzle; When adding liquid, don&rsquo;t be too full, thus the sprayerworks better; You can add perfume, milk, alcohol for other usages, just exploreby yourself, but please remember to adjust the ratio, the recommended ratio is10:1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;2.Large capacity: the 30ml storage volume can be applied about 16 to 18 times, producing a lot of mist,no need to add water frequently; Mineral water will help enhance the functionof this USB rechargeable nano sprayer, and it can last all day; Please note thisfacial mister is spraying cool mist, not hot mist</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;3.Nano sprayer: thisnano facial sprayer can be applied to nourish your face, body, hair, and can beapplied as an eyelash extender, suitable for most skin types, the nano sprayercan directly penetrate into the deep layer to achieve better absorption effect;You can add milk, perfume, toner, etc., but please remember to adjust theratio, the recommended ratio is 10:1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;4.Repairing function:when you using facial products and facial massage after sunburn, they willirritate the skin and skin feels sore and itchy, you can use our product for afew minutes, the skin will recover quickly; USB charging is also easy to use,it can be charged once a week without battery to satisfy your daily needs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;5.You will get: thepackage includes 1 pieces of portable nano facial mister in simple yet classiccolors, the size of each water tank is 10 x 4 x 4 cm/ 3.94 x 1.57 x 1.57 inchesand the capacity is 30 ml, which is suitable for home or going out, eachpackage is equipped with a USB charging cable for easy replacement, the USBcharging design makes the charging process easier</p>\r\n\r\n<p